lead_paragraph: Fathom Events and BBC Earth Films are thrilled to bring the incredible 3D nature documentary Enchanted Kingdom to cinemas nationwide for two nights on August 10 and August 11 only. To purchase your tickets, visit www.FathomEvents.com.
